OL,3,CNational Museum of Cardiff to close to
OL,4,Cthe public for a 'short period'
OL,6,FThe National Museum of Cardiff has
OL,7,Fannounced it'll close to the public
OL,8,Ffor a short period.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the museum said the
OL,11,Fneed for immediate maintenance work
OL,12,Fhad led to the "difficult decision" to
OL,13,Fclose.
OL,15,FThe museum said it was due to a
OL,16,F"mechanical issue" caused by a
OL,17,F"component failure" in an isolated
OL,18,Farea of the building.
