OL,3,CNational Museum of Cardiff to close to
OL,4,Cthe public for a 'short period'
OL,6,FThe statement read, "We are working
OL,7,Fclosely with specialists to assess the
OL,8,Fsituation and make the necessary
OL,9,Frepairs.
OL,11,FIt continued: "The safety and well-
OL,12,Fbeing of our visitors, volunteers,
OL,13,Fstaff, and the preservation of our
OL,14,Fcollections will always remain our top
OL,15,Fpriority, which is why we are taking
OL,16,Fall appropriate measures to
OL,17,Ftemporarily close the museum.
