OL,6,F"We will continue to assess the
OL,7,Fsituation and provide updates on our
OL,8,Fprogress but are hopeful that these
OL,9,Fissues will be addressed over the next
OL,10,Ffew days."
OL,12,FHeledd Fychan, Member of the Senedd
OL,13,Ffor South Wales Central and Plaid
OL,14,FCymru's spokesperson for Finance and
OL,15,FCulture, called the news "a matter of
OL,16,Freal worry."
